org.cornutum.tcases.openapi

Class InputModeller

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cornutum.tcases.openapi.ConditionReporter<OpenApiContext>
      • org.cornutum.tcases.openapi.InputModeller
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    RequestInputModeller, ResponseInputModeller

    public abstract class InputModeller
extends ConditionReporter<OpenApiContext>
    Converts between OpenAPI models and Tcases input models.

    OpenAPI models must conform to OAS version 3. See https://swagger.io/specification/#specification.
